Open your configuration file:
nano ~/.bashrc

​Find the line you wrote earlier and 
change start to y:
alias y='cd /sdcard/Download && python bot_dl.py'

​Save and Exit:
Press Ctrl + O, then Enter, then Ctrl + X.

​Refresh the shell:
source ~/.bashrc








